  .....Looking for a World Class Location for your business?.....

Then Ireland's Shannon Region has the optimal solution for you,
whether you are starting a new business or relocating an existing
business to Ireland.

Tipperary Technology Park in Thurles and Birr Technology Centre
in Co. Offaly, are part of the new Shannon Development Knowledge
Network of world-class technology locations, offering state-of-
the-art business facilities with the added bonus of being
situated in picturesque uncluttered settings. Both are designed
to support the growth and development of businesses based on
information and communication technologies

In total, 25,000 sq. ft of high quality business space on two
floors is located on the Tipperary Technology Park, while Birr
Technology Centre is a 21,000 sq. ft modernised mill building on
an attractive riverside site in the heart of Birr. The premises
at both locations are "Smart Buildings" and incorporate an
InnovationWorks facility. These are business incubation centres
designed to support new technology and knowledge-based
businesses, dedicated to exploiting the potential of new, fast
growing markets. InnovationWorks provide new businesses with a
range of support services including:

  - High quality office space and Incubation Units
  - Fully managed broadband services
  - Meeting and conference facilities
  - Business development supports
  - Office support services

Other locations in the Shannon Development Knowledge Network
include Kerry Technology Park, National Technology Park Limerick
and Information Age Park Ennis.

For further information on the Knowledge Network, Tipperary
Technology Park or Birr Technology Centre contact Mike McMahon in
Birr at 0+353-509-20440 (mailto:mcmahonm@shannondev.ie) or Brian
Keating in Thurles at +353-504-29300
(mailto:keatingb@shannondev.ie)


